******************



     Bugs concerning AmFTP should be sent to:
     The AmFTP Mailing List
     @{b}amftp@vapor.com@{ub}
     
     Bugs and corrections in the
     documentation should be sent to:
     @{b}lww@tristate.pgh.net@{ub}


